name: pipelines-in-louisiana-geographic-nad83-usgs-1999-pipelines-la-usgs-1999
notes: This dataset contains vector line map information of various pipelines throughout the State of Louisiana. The vector data contain selected base categories of geographic features, and characteristics of these features, in digital form. The information was derived from existing USGS Digital Line Graphs.
